description:
Follow the link for the latest in animal breeding

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrid3D4Ycog

http://bit.ly/Subscribe_x Click to subscribe

This tutorial will show you how to build the Animal Breeding Machine (ABM) for use in minecraft 1.2 . It works with pigs, cows, moohsrooms, sheep and cats.

Follow this link to see me build the ABM in my LP
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5fUuuNUfLUI

Lava Cooker Expansion
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OPMqMKDl7k

Thanks to H2211Games for the breeding bay fix
